---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Technical Project Lead & Delivery Management" 
  description="Account/Project Lead with Technical expertise, managing multi-stakeholder engineering projects and portfolios across SG, HK, and UK. Delivery & Release Management, coordinating across the entire software delivery lifecycle."
>

<!--
Client-facing Account/Project Lead with experience managing multi-stakeholder portfolios across SG, HK
and the UK; translating client objectives into structured plans and delivering measurable outcomes
• Data-driven communicator skilled in synthesising complex datasets into actionable recommendations
that have informed pricing, procurement and growth decisions for senior stakeholders
• Hands-on experience with Cloudflare’s developer platform (Workers, Pages, KV, R2, DNS, and Load
Balancing) to deliver performant, secure, globally distributed web and serverless applications.
--> 

  <!-- Hero Section -->
