        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet facilisi dolore vivamus fermentum platea cursus senectus.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <span class="cloud-badge">☁️ Lorem ipsum</span>
        <span class="cloud-badge">⚙️ Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">
          <span>View Projects</span>
