22:19:20 [content] Syncing content
22:19:20 [content] Synced content
22:19:20 [vite] Re-optimizing dependencies because lockfile has changed
22:19:20 [vite] Port 4321 is in use, trying another one...`}
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-output success">{`astro  v5.18.1 ready in 546 ms

┃ Local    http://localhost:4322/
┃ Network  use --host to expose

22:19:20 watching for file changes...`}<span class="cursor">.</span></div>
